{"tid":605442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無資本管制　香港樓價　熱錢　入就升　走就冧　所謂增加供應　郊野維港　社區設施　全白白犧牲","createTime":"2018-03-25T16:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T16:10:35.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"73208c351deca0e8acadea1f2360d9659e1981c1","tid":605442,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T16:10:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977429739433373696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977429739433373696&d=%2BhmjhRpiHp3B4TfzWDxdFo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=1a343790\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977429739433373696&h=84a75eba\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977429739433373696</a><br />\n<br />\n香港是一個沒有資本管制的國家，預期樓價升，資本就會流入，樓價就會升，預期樓價跌，資本就會撤，樓價就會崩。林鄭甚麼辣招都是無用的，因為不想樓價跌。而樓價跌、崩，又有另一些問題。所謂增加供應，只會不斷犧牲農地、停車場地、社區設施、綠化帶。白白犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977434629505409024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977434629505409024&d=%2BhmjhRpiHp3B4TfzWDxdFo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c1ebd8fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977434629505409024&h=e0b2960e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977434629505409024</a><br />\n<br />\n當年麥督公營房屋十年建屋計劃一出，香港樓價是崩了，當然之後回復又升。對私樓樓價，已不能做更多事。狼英、林鄭，做的事都是無用的。以前英屬港府不會這樣玩的。香港是一個沒有資本管制的國家，在中國有用的做法，在香港是無用的。香港不是中國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977438994978844675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977438994978844675&d=%2BhmjhRpiHp3B4TfzWDxdFo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7d0fd942\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977438994978844675&h=676f995c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977438994978844675</a><br />\n<br />\n年青一代面對的是沒有屬於自己個人的私人空間和睡眠空間，卻被說成置業問題。完全是狼英、林鄭置換論題。"}]}